{"tid":1894570,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"<中南海淪陷> 北京「常委級別」大人物遭感染","createTime":"2020-02-24T04:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T04:33:15.000Z","uid":240448,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3342a66c9e9abef5fa58dc4fc09716bb3887ff","tid":1894570,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:20:59.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎疫情在中國持續蔓延，現居紐約的中國反共富豪郭文貴21日直播爆料，截至21日為止，<em><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">北京大學人民醫院有超過500人遭感染，淪為北京最大的疫情爆發地點，他還爆料已有北京大人物遭感染，並透露此人黨職最低至少是「常委級別」。</span></span></strong></em><br />\n<br />\n郭文貴表示，北京大<em><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">學人民醫院絕對是中國最高級的醫院之一，擁有世界上最好的醫學設備</span></span></strong></em>，但北京大學人民醫院這回受疫情影響巨大，感染人數不斷攀升，1位來自北京大學人民醫院的內部戰友更告知他「郭先生，事大了，有人跳樓，有些人跑了，找不著了」。<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴透露，<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">北京大學人民醫院為中共提供「代孕生子」服務，是「給共產黨配種的地方」，據他所知，該醫院更是中央政治局委員、中央政治局常委、中央紀律檢查委員會、北京市紀律檢查委員會等中共要員的「定點醫院」。</span></span></em></strong><br />\n<br />\n郭文貴在直播後段進一步透露，近日他看到海外自媒體《路德社》節目主持人路德爆料北京有大人物染病，他自己也已聽聞此事，並<em><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">透露這名染病的北京大人物黨職最低至少是「常委級別」；郭文貴還爆料，聽說北京的某位名導演也已遭感染，「我說的是名導演，不是三級片的導演啊！」</span></span></strong></em><br />\n<br />\n郭文貴最後向中國人民喊話，現在疫情是<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em>「正在準備擴散中還沒開始呢」</em></span>，呼籲中國人民千萬要採取防護措施，做好更壞、更長的時間準備。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞請見︰<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎懶人包》傳染途徑、預防措施看這裡<br />\n「武漢肺炎專區」請點此，更多相關訊息，帶您第一手掌握。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xq9U828.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxq9U828.png&h=3bd5ab17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33c2cd661b0d7bfdbe2b00330c1f357ebf0dfeec","tid":1894570,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:21:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3077236\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3077236&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAs2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=239e2cf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3077236&h=5ec1d5f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3077236</a>"},{"pid":"9122e59ec7262bbd8304f5ce26db775c427c5e32","tid":1894570,"uid":57862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:22:46.000Z","msg":"唔怪得要中南海要走佬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2bd86c9bea021d28ca9251c8447d68c06f9c459","tid":1894570,"uid":270506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KgF5whz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKgF5whz.jpg&h=60626189&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52c4ae3577c9818bb8d3a1132b00049347961f6e","tid":1894570,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9122e59ec7262bbd8304f5ce26db775c427c5e32","tid":1894570,"uid":57862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:22:46.000Z","msg":"唔怪得要中南海要走佬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958d4158c9990b887387748eb32d5dc47c8caeaa","tid":1894570,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1c9114a87f19677c352986cb259f1b66ceee20","tid":1894570,"uid":211121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:24:52.000Z","msg":"范"},{"pid":"47deffc68e29169d9e59fe282004258ee0e03e57","tid":1894570,"uid":191812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"